race.comment: EVERY HEART (7) deserved her easy CL1 win at Eagle Farm. Has placed this course/distance and keeps improving. In good hands and can go on with the job. VOS SAVANT (9) was nudged out in a CL3 at Eagle Farm and then went back and did a good job beaten 2L over 1500m, after settling at the rear. She can sit closer today and deserves another chance. ARATIRI (11) looked a run short beaten 2L here first-up in a CL4. Races forward and has more to give over the longer sprint. Well in the mix. ORIENTE (1) rates similarly, and his Eagle Farm win two back reads well.
